
Gentlemen's Agreement for this legacy code:
===========================================

If you are modifying the files contained in this source code package you
agree to keep in mind the following rules:

a) Do not change or delete lines of citations of previous authors.
b) Maintain the modification history with your authorship.
c) Keep additions to the code in about the same formal style as it is now.

Thanks for your cooperation.

Urs Rohrer (PSI), July 2007
